\end{eqnarray*}
picturing expression \( Cons(2,Cons(1,Nil)) \).
$Nil$ is the empty tree and $Cons$ may be regarded as the operation which
adds a new root and a new branch, say $a$, to a tree $t$:
\begin{eqnarray*}
