R \mbox{\ is simple}
&
\equiv
&
\img{R} \subseteq id
\label{eq:020605f}
\end{eqnarray*}
%that is, $\img R$ is coreflexive.

Simplicity is the dual of entireness. Simple relations are also called \textbf{partial functions}.
\end{Slide}

